{"tid":357030,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"屋企養貓，有冇人知邊到買貓窗花平？","createTime":"2017-08-12T14:33:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-13T15:02:09.000Z","uid":134142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8121eedade06d229e461b2c52164f5c0f19d2cee","tid":357030,"uid":134142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T14:33:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/12/222858_6906f17a4a1a42817b6815f06c866d14.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F12%2F222858_6906f17a4a1a42817b6815f06c866d14.jpg&h=7c8f8ac3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n想買依款窗花 因為屋企人要晾衫 有冇養貓嘅巴絲知邊到買平 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c4309a4ad05983e42e7953e773bb1fe633fd961","tid":357030,"uid":122807,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T14:42:17.000Z","msg":"最平都係12蚊店格仔網"},{"pid":"4174e9b380fb54a6d07d0b29c264eb60df984b35","tid":357030,"uid":16061,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T14:57:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最平都係12蚊店格仔網</blockquote><br />\n人地講到明要呢類窗花<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47e5f8bcf8f712deed2d9710397dc02deb51fd2c","tid":357030,"uid":134142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T15:42:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最平都係12蚊店格仔網</blockquote><br />\n晾唔到衫屋企人話唔得"},{"pid":"421d26305637f43294df047a37b936c66ce10442","tid":357030,"uid":15309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T17:15:29.000Z","msg":"買個格仔網 剪斷斷條咪晾到衫"},{"pid":"de6e36b26e7051366c0c554dcf12ea0a5a52b893","tid":357030,"uid":15309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T17:15:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>買個格仔網 剪斷<span style=\"color: red;\">幾</span>條咪晾到衫</blockquote>"},{"pid":"275aa8a581bb4f0e6ca781dc2e0d3426cb9c9262","tid":357030,"uid":7119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T17:59:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/12/222858_6906f17a4a1a42817b6815f06c866d14.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F12%2F222858_6906f17a4a1a42817b6815f06c866d14.jpg&h=7c8f8ac3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n想買依款窗花 因為屋企人要晾衫 有冇養貓嘅巴絲知邊到買平 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你呢款都普通窗花有咩分別<br />\n條gap一樣夠過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"925ff41af86c122aa6623468ff29eddb2a82a9bd","tid":357030,"uid":21654,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T03:25:02.000Z","msg":"最好唔過2吋，如果讓幼貓更加唔過1.5吋<br />\n自己落街鋪揾啦，你要度尺，而且呢啲窗花唔會平，用料已經多左<br />\n如果唔係外觀問題格仔網可以整活頁，用文件夾夾住，用嘅時候打外"},{"pid":"80b11d106f9055fb6c9cbd30fc01a9646293f755","tid":357030,"uid":125000,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T14:58:16.000Z","msg":"之前紅磡有間係買活動窗花~$200左右<br />\n唔包送，唔包裝<br />\n但諗到屋企有成8隻窗即刻打消念頭"},{"pid":"310cb6b2dccdeb8821a3f574c2af7d3390920a5d","tid":357030,"uid":1188,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T15:02:09.000Z","msg":"91972093<br />\n呢款我搵呢個師傅裝 價錢唔記得<br />\n問問佢啦"}]}